    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a separate baking tray (or two!) with <strong>non-stick baking paper </strong>and dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry</strong> and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> and cut into 1 rectangle per person</p><p>Add the <strong>pastry</strong> to the tray[s] and score a 1cm border around the edge of the pastry with a knife</p><p>Prick the inside of the border all over with a fork</p>",
