    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the pastry with the <strong>chopped basa </strong>then spoon over the<strong> curried cheesy corn</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 18-20 min or until the pastry is golden and cooked through and the filling is bubbling and golden – this is your <strong>curried, cheesy corn & smoked basa tartlet</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p><p>Meanwhile, trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
