      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> baby leaf salad</strong>, then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper</p><p>Drizzle a little <strong>olive oil </strong>and your<strong> white wine vinegar </strong>over the <strong>baby leaf salad </strong>– this is your<strong> dressed salad</strong></p><p>Top the<strong> curried, cheesy corn & smoked basa tartlet </strong>with the<strong> sliced spring onion </strong>and serve the <strong>dressed salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
